caption: Absolute silence and peaceful atmosphere. You can see the corpse of St Vincent de Paul in this chapel. You can go nearby his body and praying there is possible. The chapel is very nice and the arrangements are great. Most of the people don't know about this place . This place is usually less occupied when you are going between 14:00 - 16:30.

One of the best places to pray and meditate in silence, in one of the most profound and symbolic religious sites in the world. Just one block away from the Chapel of the Miraculous Medallion. Access to the body of Saint Vincent is easy if you walk all the way back behind the altar. You will see stairs that lead up to the place where the body is resting.
